"   <div class=\"ttl\">",
"    Triquetral fracture on lateral plain x-ray",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"cntnt\" style=\"width: 288px; height: 384px; background-image: url(data:image/jpeg;base64,);\">",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"lgnd\">",
"    In this lateral radiograph of the wrist, a fracture of the dorsal surface of the triquetrum is apparent (arrow).",
"    <div class=\"footnotes\">",
"    </div>",
"    <div class=\"reference\">",
"     Courtesy of Kevin E Burroughs, MD.",
"    </div>",
"   </div>",
"  </div>",
" </div>",
" <div class=\"graphic\">",
"  <div class=\"figure\" style=\"width: 470px\">",
"   <div class=\"ttl\">",
"    Triquetral fracture on oblique x-ray",
"   </div>",
